name: Alpha Deeds (No land included. See Description for more details.)

metadata.name: Founders Deed #00001
metadata.description: Each Founders Deed holder is granted the deed to a fully customizable world, and given the power to connect it to the LeapN multiverse. Additional utility for the Deed holder will include: access to park your 'world' in Founders Cove (prime real estate in the LeapN multiverse), 'pay-per-visit' visitability upgrade for explorers in the multiverse, and several other exciting features to be detailed in LeapN's discord server. Find out more: [leapn.life](https://leapn.life)
